OL,3,CContractors plead not guilty over
OL,4,Cdeath of Hinkley Point C worker
OL,6,FThree companies have pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to health and safety offences
OL,8,Fafter a worker died at Hinkley Point C
OL,9,Fin Somerset in 2022.
OL,11,FNNB Generation Company (HPC) Ltd,
OL,12,FBouygues Travaux Publics SAS and Laing
OL,13,FO'Rourke Delivery Limited appeared at
OL,14,FBristol Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,15,F15 December.
OL,17,FThe prosecution was brought by the
OL,18,FOffice for Nuclear Regulation (ONR),
OL,19,Fthe UK's independent nuclear regulator.
