OL,3,CContractors plead not guilty over
OL,4,Cdeath of Hinkley Point C worker
OL,6,FIt relates to an incident at Hinkley
OL,7,FPoint C near Bridgwater on 13 November
OL,8,F2022.
OL,10,FSite supervisor Jason Waring, who was
OL,11,F48, died after sustaining fatal
OL,12,Finjuries in a construction incident.
OL,14,FNNB Generation Company (HPC) Ltd (NNB
OL,15,FGenCo) entered a not guilty plea to
OL,16,Ffailing to plan, manage and monitor
OL,17,Fthe construction phase, and co-
OL,18,Fordinate matters relating to health
OL,19,Fand safety during the construction
OL,20,Fphase, to ensure that work was carried
OL,21,Fout without risks to health and safety.
