OL,3,CContractors plead not guilty over
OL,4,Cdeath of Hinkley Point C worker
OL,6,FBouygues Travaux Publics SAS and Laing
OL,7,FO'Rourke Delivery Limited entered not
OL,8,Fguilty pleas to failing to plan,
OL,9,Fmanage and monitor to ensure that
OL,10,Fconstruction work was carried out
OL,11,Fwithout risks to health and safety.
OL,13,FNNB GenCo is the main contractor for
OL,14,Fthe ongoing nuclear construction
OL,15,Fproject.
