OL,3,CContractors plead not guilty over
OL,4,Cdeath of Hinkley Point C worker
OL,6,FContractors Bouygues Travaux Publics
OL,7,FSAS and Laing O'Rourke Delivery
OL,8,FLimited are the joint venture partners
OL,9,Fin BYLOR JV, the two companies
OL,10,Fdelivering the main civil engineering
OL,11,Fworks at Hinkley Point C.
OL,13,FThis matter will now progress to trial
OL,14,Fand the case was adjourned until 30
OL,15,FJanuary at Bristol Crown Court for a
OL,16,Fpre-trial review hearing.
